	- The Duchy of Cloudbury can now restore and puppet the Northern Tribes if they're subjugated by Skynavia
CHANGES:
	- Improved Famine mechanics
	- Rosewing's ideology after victory in the power struggle is Reactionarism instead of fascism
	- Completely overhauled the Republic's military bonuses into a single upgradeable Republican Army national spirit
FIXES:
	- Republican Railroads industrial concern no longer available for the Duchy of Cloudbury
